        <mxCell id="X4k6HF8neTEFMJo-2yWl-5" parent="1" style="text;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;" value="&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;aa2xz8&quot; data-start=&quot;153&quot; data-end=&quot;216&quot;&gt;User should be allowed to create account in our application&#xa;&lt;/li&gt;&#xa;&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;1tbfvn8&quot; data-start=&quot;217&quot; data-end=&quot;295&quot;&gt;&#xa;Users can upload (resumed/disconnected) and download files of various size&#xa;&lt;/li&gt;&#xa;&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;86c5xm&quot; data-start=&quot;296&quot; data-end=&quot;345&quot;&gt;&#xa;Changes sync across all devices automatically&#xa;&lt;/li&gt;&#xa;&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;1rpg5q0&quot; data-start=&quot;346&quot; data-end=&quot;427&quot;&gt;&#xa;User should be able to share files/folders with other users (with permission)&#xa;&lt;/li&gt;&#xa;&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;1wa3shf&quot; data-start=&quot;428&quot; data-end=&quot;504&quot;&gt;&#xa;User should be able to create, delete, rename folders and organize files&#xa;&lt;/li&gt;&#xa;&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;z56fkk&quot; data-start=&quot;505&quot; data-end=&quot;547&quot;&gt;&#xa;Quota / storage limit: per user quotas&lt;/li&gt;" vertex="1">
